name: Regain
description:
in the battle of countless darkness
it exists in its absence

wherever he sees this world
where there is light there will always be a shadow

nothing goes according to plan in this world
the reward for ambition to great... is self destruction

is he living his dreams in death or...  is death the end of dreams
to understand pain
man must suffer

and to learn a  way to survive in the darkness where the light of that order does not reach
the one and only things... 
is. certain.

REGAIN
